&lt;h2 id="1-notion-ai"&gt;1. Notion AI&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="what-is-notion-ai"&gt;What is Notion AI?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Notion AI is an all-in-one workspace that integrates notes, tasks, databases, and project management. With AI capabilities, it enhances these features by automating repetitive tasks, generating content, and organizing information seamlessly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="use-cases"&gt;Use Cases&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Generation&lt;/strong&gt;: Need to draft an article? Notion AI can help generate outlines or entire sections based on your prompts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Automatically update project statuses and remind team members of deadlines using AI-generated task lists.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="pros-and-cons"&gt;Pros and Cons&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Pros&lt;/th&gt;
