&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-trello-with-butler-ai"&gt;2. Trello with Butler AI&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="what-is-trello-with-butler-ai"&gt;What is Trello with Butler AI?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trello is a popular project management tool that uses boards, lists, and cards to organize tasks. Butler, an AI-powered automation tool within Trello, takes this a step further by automating repetitive tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="use-cases-1"&gt;Use Cases&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Task Automation&lt;/strong&gt;: Automatically move cards between lists based on due dates or project milestones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Custom Alerts&lt;/strong&gt;: Set up notifications for team members when a task is updated or a deadline is approaching.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
