&lt;h2 id="3-clockify-ai"&gt;3. Clockify AI&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="what-is-clockify-ai"&gt;What is Clockify AI?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clockify is a time tracking tool that helps teams and individuals understand how much time they spend on tasks. With its AI features, it can analyze your time usage and suggest optimizations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="use-cases-2"&gt;Use Cases&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time Analysis&lt;/strong&gt;: Clockify can automatically categorize tasks and provide insights into where you can save time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Productivity Reports&lt;/strong&gt;: Generate weekly reports that show your most productive hours and tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
