&lt;h2 id="5-todoist-with-ai-features"&gt;5. Todoist with AI Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="what-is-todoist"&gt;What is Todoist?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Todoist is a task management app that helps users keep track of their to-do lists and projects. The AI features allow for smart scheduling and task prioritization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="use-cases-4"&gt;Use Cases&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart Scheduling&lt;/strong&gt;: Todoist can suggest the best times to complete tasks based on your habits and deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
